    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Hemigrammus parana, holotype, DZSJRP 6217, 24.9 mm SL, rio Grande, near the old port of sand, known as Velho Adão, municipality of Santa Clara D’Oeste, São Paulo state, upper rio Paraná drainage, Brazil." ;
